        <detaileddescription>
<para>Duplicates rate term and then applies volume scaling. Arguments are volume of reference voxel, product of vol/refVol for all substrates: applied to R1 product of vol/refVol for all products: applied to R2</para>
<para>Note that unless the reaction is cross-compartment, the vol/refVol will be one. </para>
        </detaileddescription>
